# Privacy: real-people briefs (named persons) must NOT be committed to the
# public repo. Real briefs are local-only by convention — see
# personas/real-people/README.md.
# Allowed in the repo: README.md, index.md, opt-outs.md, TEMPLATE.md.
personas/real-people/*.md
!personas/real-people/README.md
!personas/real-people/index.md
!personas/real-people/opt-outs.md
!personas/real-people/TEMPLATE.md
